#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.109"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.109:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.109:0.2"
msgid "11. Sambodhavagga "
msgstr "11. Awakening "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.109:0.3"
msgid "109. Arakkhitasutta "
msgstr "109. Unprotected "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.109:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.109:1.2"
msgid "“citte, gahapati, arakkhite kāyakammampi arakkhitaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi arakkhitaṃ hoti, manokammampi arakkhitaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "“Householder, when the mind is unprotected, deeds of body, speech, and mind are unprotected. "

msgctxt "an3.109:1.3"
msgid "Tassa arakkhitakāyakammantassa arakkhitavacīkammantassa arakkhitamanokammantassa kāyakammampi avassutaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi avassutaṃ hoti, manokammampi avassutaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When deeds are unprotected, they become corrupted. "

msgctxt "an3.109:1.4"
msgid "Tassa avassutakāyakammantassa avassutavacīkammantassa avassutamanokammantassa kāyakammampi pūtikaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi pūtikaṃ hoti, manokammampi pūtikaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When deeds are corrupted, they become rotten. "

msgctxt "an3.109:1.5"
msgid "Tassa pūtikāyakammantassa pūtivacīkammantassa pūtimanokammantassa na bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, na bhaddikā kālakiriyā. "
msgstr "Someone whose deeds of body, speech, and mind are rotten will not have a good death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.109:2.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, gahapati, kūṭāgāre ducchanne kūṭampi arakkhitaṃ hoti, gopānasiyopi arakkhitā honti, bhittipi arakkhitā hoti; "
msgstr "It’s like a bungalow with a bad roof. The roof peak, rafters, and walls are unprotected. "

msgctxt "an3.109:2.2"
msgid "kūṭampi avassutaṃ hoti, gopānasiyopi avassutā honti, bhittipi avassutā hoti; "
msgstr "They get soaked, "

msgctxt "an3.109:2.3"
msgid "kūṭampi pūtikaṃ hoti, gopānasiyopi pūtikā honti, bhittipi pūtikā hoti. "
msgstr "and become rotten. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.262, sc3
msgctxt "an3.109:3.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, gahapati, citte arakkhite kāyakammampi arakkhitaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi arakkhitaṃ hoti, manokammampi arakkhitaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "In the same way, when the mind is unprotected, bodily, verbal, and mental deeds are unprotected. … "

msgctxt "an3.109:3.2"
msgid "Tassa arakkhitakāyakammantassa arakkhitavacīkammantassa arakkhitamanokammantassa kāyakammampi avassutaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi avassutaṃ hoti, manokammampi avassutaṃ hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.109:3.3"
msgid "Tassa avassutakāyakammantassa avassutavacīkammantassa avassutamanokammantassa kāyakammampi pūtikaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi pūtikaṃ hoti, manokammampi pūtikaṃ hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.109:3.4"
msgid "Tassa pūtikāyakammantassa pūtivacīkammantassa pūtimanokammantassa na bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, na bhaddikā kālakiriyā. "
msgstr "Someone whose deeds of body, speech, and mind are rotten will not have a good death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an3.109:4.1"
msgid "Citte, gahapati, rakkhite kāyakammampi rakkhitaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi rakkhitaṃ hoti, manokammampi rakkhitaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When the mind is protected, bodily, verbal, and mental deeds are protected. "

msgctxt "an3.109:4.2"
msgid "Tassa rakkhitakāyakammantassa rakkhitavacīkammantassa rakkhitamanokammantassa kāyakammampi anavassutaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi anavassutaṃ hoti, manokammampi anavassutaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When deeds are protected, they don’t become corrupted. "

msgctxt "an3.109:4.3"
msgid "Tassa anavassutakāyakammantassa anavassutavacīkammantassa anavassutamanokammantassa kāyakammampi apūtikaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi apūtikaṃ hoti, manokammampi apūtikaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When deeds aren’t corrupted, they don’t become rotten. "

msgctxt "an3.109:4.4"
msgid "Tassa apūtikāyakammantassa apūtivacīkammantassa apūtimanokammantassa bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, bhaddikā kālakiriyā. "
msgstr "Someone whose deeds of body, speech, and mind aren’t rotten will have a good death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an3.109:5.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, gahapati, kūṭāgāre succhanne kūṭampi rakkhitaṃ hoti, gopānasiyopi rakkhitā honti, bhittipi rakkhitā hoti; "
msgstr "It’s like a bungalow with a good roof. The roof peak, rafters, and walls are protected. "

msgctxt "an3.109:5.2"
msgid "kūṭampi anavassutaṃ hoti, gopānasiyopi anavassutā honti, bhittipi anavassutā hoti; "
msgstr "They don’t get soaked, "

msgctxt "an3.109:5.3"
msgid "kūṭampi apūtikaṃ hoti, gopānasiyopi apūtikā honti, bhittipi apūtikā hoti. "
msgstr "and they don’t become rotten. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an3.109:6.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, gahapati, citte rakkhite kāyakammampi rakkhitaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi rakkhitaṃ hoti, manokammampi rakkhitaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "In the same way, when the mind is protected, bodily, verbal, and mental deeds are protected. … "

msgctxt "an3.109:6.2"
msgid "Tassa rakkhitakāyakammantassa rakkhitavacīkammantassa rakkhitamanokammantassa kāyakammampi anavassutaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi anavassutaṃ hoti, manokammampi anavassutaṃ hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.109:6.3"
msgid "Tassa anavassutakāyakammantassa anavassutavacīkammantassa anavassutamanokammantassa kāyakammampi apūtikaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi apūtikaṃ hoti, manokammampi apūtikaṃ hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.109:6.4"
msgid "Tassa apūtikāyakammantassa apūtivacīkammantassa apūtimanokammantassa bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, bhaddikā kālakiriyā”ti. "
msgstr "Someone whose deeds of body, speech, and mind aren’t rotten will have a good death.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.109:6.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

